This paper deals with graph theory and combinatorics, specifically focusing on independent sets and critical sets in bipartite graphs. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), followed by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory). The paper also involves computational geometry, which falls under cs.CG (Computational Geometry), and graph algorithms, which falls under cs.CC (Computational Complexity).
